*----------------------------------------------------------------------
* test/fence_function/t01_basic_match.sno
* FENCE(P) basic: P matches -> overall match succeeds
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
*   FENCE(P) should match exactly as P would when P succeeds on
*   first try with no backtracking needed.
*----------------------------------------------------------------------
               S = 'hello'
               S  FENCE('hello')                            :F(FAIL)
               OUTPUT = 'PASS t01: FENCE(P) basic match'   :(END)
FAIL           OUTPUT = 'FAIL t01: FENCE(P) basic match'
END
